➜江西诗人时差先生：河床
http://www.sohu.com/a/433205333_100115135	42284
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201120/c27eee7c9965493b931265ea8c2c7a06.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>河床</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/时差先生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雨水干了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋风口亦老了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">江河温柔的曲线</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不再蔓延</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">留下一身唯美的瘦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水盼望恋爱的季节</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">做了春的情人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唯有冬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唱起枯燥的单曲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">守候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个又一个流年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201120/4d2ad2796dd04f33830e79bd7d11b908.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
